  "name": "RPlog_The_Mission_the_Fracas",
  "title": "The Mission, the Fracas",
  "summary": "In a snow-covered commerce square on a Caspian capital world, the Imperial agent Danik Kreldin lures the Dark Jedi Ezkhil into a trap, having tipped off the Imperial Ground Forces to his location. As Danik draws and fires, an airborne skiff carrying a strike team led by Lieutenant Ashby Williams and the officer Lanil drops concussion grenades and fast-ropes troopers into the square. Ezkhil ignites his golden lightsaber and turns the assault into a rout, deflecting blaster bolts back into the skiff until it crashes in flames and hurling troopers into the fountain. Danik snipes at the Jedi from a pub window only to be flung out by the Force, and with police constables and CDU forces closing in, he radios for evacuation and orders a retreat. The battered Imperials flee to their landing zone, detonating explosives to cover their escape, while Ezkhil slips away north. The aftermath, reported as a terrorist firefight leaving twenty-seven dead, sees Marines later hunting down the surviving gunmen.",
